<SYNC Start=255078><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=255321><P Class=ENCC>
What does he want with her?
<SYNC Start=257084><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=257323><P Class=ENCC>
