<SYNC Start=259416><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=261494><P Class=ENCC>
...you know, make a little love....
<SYNC Start=263724><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=266666><P Class=ENCC>
Well, get down tonight.
<SYNC Start=268156><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=274574><P Class=ENCC>
I don't know. I don't
<SYNC Start=275871><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=276109><P Class=ENCC>
I don't get it! Two months ago,<br>Rachel and I were this close.
<SYNC Start=279704><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=279912><P Class=ENCC>
Now I'm taking messages from guys<br>she meets at the movies?
<SYNC Start=283348><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=283549><P Class=ENCC>
