<SYNC Start=301229><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=303536><P Class=ENCC>
Oh, she's going somewhere.
<SYNC Start=305026><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=307273><P Class=ENCC>
