<SYNC Start=315974><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=316249><P Class=ENCC>
...walking around their tank,<br>holding claws, like....
<SYNC Start=319946><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=324090><P Class=ENCC>
Hey, you feeling better?
<SYNC Start=325648><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=325892><P Class=ENCC>
