<SYNC Start=371095><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=373940><P Class=ENCC>
Man, that is sharp! That must<br>have cost you quite a few doubloons.
<SYNC Start=378104><P Class=ENCC>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=384016><P Class=ENCC>
